    "Leaving the distinctive blue hues of the Igreja de São Lourenço, we journey towards the natural embrace of Ria Formosa Natural Park. This stretch of coastal lagoon, extending over sixty kilometers along the Algarve coastline, is a network of ecosystems that has earned its place among Portugal's Seven Natural Wonders." /
